body: By the way, since `reshape` is migrated from `_gen_array_op` to `array_op`, should we remove the duplicate document of `_gen_array_op._reshape`? If I understand correctly, the description is in the [tensorflow/core/ops/ops.pbtxt](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/ca1f9846a1fa6056c28b6512e3dd1037132ef7af/tensorflow/core/ops/ops.pbtxt#L19593)
